title: SELVA PODCAST TUESDAY 040621

description:
Jets trade Darnold to Panthers for 3 draft picks. Titans key additions on defense, plus Vrabel sound on those additions. Penei Sewell talks to Sports Illustrated about how exciting joining the Chargers would be, and they have been in talks. Lions ink Quinton Dunbar to one year deal.
